# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Secrets
# .env.example is intentionally included here (no carve-out) — it was previously tracked as a
# template with blank placeholders, but real secrets were pasted into it and committed at least
# once (2026-07-20 incident: a TOGETHER_API_KEY + SENTRY_DSN reached a pushed backup branch).
# Since .gitignore alone cannot stop `git add -A` from re-staging edits to an *already-tracked*
# file, it was also untracked (`git rm --cached`) so this can't recur regardless of file content.
.env
.env.*
credentials.toml
AIMLAPI_APIkey_d7b094b8.txt
*.pem
*.key

